snippet.title: Stories From a Van
snippet.description:
Hi! My name is Evan and I live in my self-converted van in Santa Cruz, California! Join me as I build community through storytelling!

Meet me in person along with others that follow the channel!
https://forms.gle/hzJKNno9Ttt542Gq9

Join the Online Community!
Discord: https://discord.gg/KgZSBSaXnK

Social Media
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/storiesfromavan
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/storiesfromavan
Twitter: https://twitter.com/van_stories

Help support the channel and community!
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/storiesfromavan

Contact
email: storiesfromavan@gmail.com
